  "title": "Meteor templating(Blaze) won't work inside widgets",
  "body": "I got the [tutorial](https://demo.algolia.com/instant-search-demo/) code to work by using a Mustache String template(see below) and now I want to include a Meteor template inside the hits div but it does not work. Specifically, I want to include an \"add to shopping cart\" button right below the description but I cannot use Meteor templates inside the hits div so I can't add  a button. Can you please help?\n\nHere is the code for my main.js: \n\n<img width=\"921\" alt=\"screenshot 2016-07-05 00 35 18\" src=\"https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/19519903/16570135/628504f6-4248-11e6-877c-9c177df3f045.png\">\n\nHere is the code I am using for the {{test}} template helper. It just returns the string \"test\" when {{test}} is called: \n\n<img width=\"272\" alt=\"screenshot 2016-07-05 00 45 50\" src=\"https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/19519903/16570205/d89b4bc2-4249-11e6-9eab-6106ebf01be9.png\">\n",
